  "title": "Junior Brand Development (ASAP, Fresh Grads Welcome!)",
  "description": "<p><strong>🌟 Junior Brand Development (ASAP, Fresh Grads Welcomed)</strong></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Ready to kickstart your career in a fun and energetic environment? Join our <strong>Junior Brand Development Crew</strong> — where you’ll represent exciting brands, meet new people, and grow your skills through hands-on experience. No experience? No problem! We provide full training and mentorship.</p>\n<h3><strong>What You’ll Do</strong></h3>\n<p>✨ Represent and promote brands at events, business campaigns<br>\n🤝 Engage customers with positivity and enthusiasm<br>\n🎯 Support team goals and create great brand experiences<br>\n💡 Learn marketing and communication skills along the way</p>\n<h3><strong>What You’ll Get</strong></h3>\n<p>✅ Immediate start &amp; full training provided<br>\n✅ Supportive team and fun work culture<br>\n✅ Clear career growth opportunities<br>\n✅ Fixed hours + performance incentives<br>\n✅ Fresh grads &amp; ORD candidates welcome!</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>If you’re outgoing, eager for growth, and ready to start something new —</p>\n<p><br>\n📩 <strong>Apply now and grow with us as part of our Brand Development Crew!</strong></p>",
